author: Reuters Editorial
title: REFILE-BRIEF-Shenzhen Heungkong's 2017 Net Profit Up 18.3 Percent Y/Y At 816.6 Million Yuan
text:
(Refiles to add link and bullet point)
April 10 (Reuters) - Shenzhen Heungkong Holding Co Ltd :
* SAYS 2017 NET PROFIT UP 18.3 PERCENT Y/Y AT 816.6 MILLION YUAN ($129.92 million)
* SAYS IT PLANS TO INVEST ABOUT 5.5 BILLION YUAN IN PROPERTY PROJECTS IN 2018 Source text in Chinese: bit.ly/2HaixqT ; bit.ly/2Hn4AUc Further company coverage: ($1 = 6.2853 Chinese yuan renminbi) (Reporting by Hong Kong newsroom)
